            "由条件可知 $\\overrightarrow{AF_{1}}\\cdot \\overrightarrow{AF_{2}} + \\overrightarrow{BF_{1}}\\cdot \\overrightarrow{BF_{2}} = (-c-a)(c-a) + (-c^{2} + b^{2}) = a^{2} + b^{2} - 2c^{2} = 0$",
            "所以 $\\frac{|AB|}{|F_{1}F_{2}|} = \\frac{\\sqrt{a^{2} + b^{2}}}{2c} = \\frac{\\sqrt{2}}{2}$"
        ],
        "final_answer": ["$\\frac{\\sqrt{2}}{2}$"],
