        "question": "设 $z$ 为复数，若 $\\frac{z-2}{z-\\mathrm{i}}$ 为实数（i为虚数单位），则 $|z+3|$ 的最小值为______。",
        "solution": [
            "设 $z = a + b\\mathrm{i}$（$a,b \\in \\mathbb{R}$），由条件可知",
            "$\\operatorname{Im}(\\frac{z-2}{z-\\mathrm{i}}) = \\operatorname{Im}(\\frac{(a-2) + b\\mathrm{i}}{a + (b-1)\\mathrm{i}}) = \\frac{-(a-2)(b-1) + ab}{a^{2} + (b-1)^{2}} = \\frac{a + 2b - 2}{a^{2} + (b-1)^{2}} = 0$",
            "故 $a + 2b = 2$，从而",
            "$\\sqrt{5}|z + 3| = \\sqrt{(1^{2} + 2^{2})((a+3)^{2} + b^{2})} \\geq |a + 3 + 2b| = 5$",
            "即 $|z + 3| \\geq \\sqrt{5}$",
            "当 $a = -2, b = 2$ 时，$|z + 3|$ 取到最小值 $\\sqrt{5}$"
        ],
        "final_answer": ["$\\sqrt{5}$"],
        "is_multiple_answer": false,
        "unit": null,
        "answer_type": "Expression",
        "error": null
    },
