        "context": "2020年全国高中数学联合竞赛A卷解答题",
        "question": "对正整数 $n$ 及实数 $x$（$0\\leq x < n$），定义 $f(n,x) = (1 - \\{x\\}) \\cdot \\binom{[x]}{n} + \\{x\\} \\cdot \\binom{[x] + 1}{n}$，其中 $[x]$ 表示不超过实数 $x$ 的最大整数，$\\{x\\} = x - [x]$。若整数 $m,n\\geq 2$ 满足 $f(m,\\frac{1}{n}) + f(m,\\frac{2}{n}) + \\dots + f(m,\\frac{mn-1}{n}) = 123$，求 $f(n,\\frac{1}{m}) + f(n,\\frac{2}{m}) + \\dots + f(n,\\frac{mn-1}{m})$ 的值。",
        "solution": [
            "对 $k = 0,1,\\dots,m-1$，有",
            "$\\sum_{i=1}^{n-1}f(m, k + \\frac{i}{n}) = \\binom{m}{k} \\cdot \\sum_{i=1}^{n-1}(1 - \\frac{i}{n}) + \\binom{m}{k+1} \\cdot \\sum_{i=1}^{n-1}\\frac{i}{n} = \\frac{n-1}{2} \\cdot \\binom{m}{k} + \\binom{m}{k+1}$",
            "于是",
            "$g(m,n) = f(m,\\frac{1}{n}) + f(m,\\frac{2}{n}) + \\dots + f(m,\\frac{mn-1}{n})$",
            "$= \\sum_{j=1}^{m-1}\\binom{m}{j} + \\sum_{k=0}^{m-1}\\sum_{i=1}^{n-1}f(m, k + \\frac{i}{n})$",
            "$= 2^{m} - 2 + \\frac{n-1}{2} \\cdot (\\sum_{k=0}^{m-1}\\binom{m}{k} + \\sum_{k=0}^{m-1}\\binom{m}{k+1})$",
            "$= 2^{m} - 2 + \\frac{n-1}{2} \\cdot (2^{m} - 1 + 2^{m} - 1)$",
            "$= (2^{m} - 1)n - 1$",
            "根据题意，有 $(2^{m} - 1)n - 1 = 123 \\iff (2^{m} - 1)n = 2^{2} \\cdot 31$",
            "于是 $m = 5$，$n = 4$，从而",
            "$f(n,\\frac{1}{m}) + f(n,\\frac{2}{m}) + \\cdots + f(n,\\frac{mn-1}{m}) = g(n,m) = (2^{n} - 1)m - 1 = (2^{4} - 1) \\cdot 5 - 1 = 74$"
        ],
        "final_answer": ["74"],
        "is_multiple_answer": false,
        "unit": null,
        "answer_type": "Numerical",
        "error": null
    },
